Package com.example.StudentManagement.entity

Class Coursework

java.lang.Object
com.example.StudentManagement.entity.Coursework
public class Coursework extends Object
This class represents a Coursework entity in the application. It has properties to store coursework information such as assessmentID, title, deadline, moduleCode, grade, feedback, filePath, and studentID.
Author:
Jiaming LIU
